Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在笑著…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}預備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}預備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}身體好點了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 漸漸好點了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}結果怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要恢復過來挺辛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哇 傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 我是短跑的松田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是跨欄的永井
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是兵藤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 我是雪哉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好了 柳 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嘿 居然都到互相叫名字的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雪哉 別被女孩吸乾了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}各位也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}積蓄太多是會影響成績的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}前些時的煙火大會好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 我好想去看的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明年一定要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.85,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那煙火放得很近的 好大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.08,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雖然聽不太懂不過好厲害的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說那種話沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}會有流言蜚語的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}讓他們說去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我突然想起件事 先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}請問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}難不成小祐今天也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}去約會了 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}冒昧問一句 他是在跟誰約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也不會那麼清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你是叫透子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你最近也越來越有女人味了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}夏日是戀愛的季節嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哎呀我真是的 怎麼能對客人說這種話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒事沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}作為賠禮 我請你吃餅乾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過… 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}上次多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就為了這麼一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}特地追得氣喘吁吁的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想跟你說幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你肯定做過這種事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}對著美術室裡素描用的石膏像說話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}來整理自己的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子可是做過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那我不答話也沒問題是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸 在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 透子來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 今天她要來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我能進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等等哦 我這就下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大概是我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 那我去打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}待會再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪在高一的夏天時傷到了腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}現在在康復訓練中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天還去參加了附近初高中合辦的個人紀錄賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過成績不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}聽說小祐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天去約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我還以為肯定是和小幸約會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是今天都說好了要來找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸 你在和小祐交往嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}他剛才還在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}感覺今天都是讓我吃驚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過 真沒想到你們倆都已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}進展到這般地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我沒說我們在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天也只是一起在這裡讀書而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過如此而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒是透子 從那以後你還在跟那個人見面什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沖倉他雖然看著挺嚴肅的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過多少也有他溫柔的一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}畢竟是個帥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不是這麼回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不是這麼回事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我最近要住幾天院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}只是住院檢查而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}完全不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}然後呢 出院以後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我有個想和透子一起去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}還不能告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是能看見未來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}總覺得小雪現在很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過大家也都想知道未來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真的一句話都不想說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是 我是不會看的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 這裡是沖倉家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 沖倉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是深水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能見個面嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有點事情想拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那天晚上你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我認真考慮過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個 驅的話現在不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呃 不好意思現在才跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是驅的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等他回來了我會告訴他的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸～！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…我先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說好了不要隨便進來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這是什麼書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒什麼沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}只是偶爾也想讀讀書而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你買的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你這小子怎麼可能會看加繆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}加繆啊加繆 還他媽是薛西弗斯神話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}扯淡啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是那個紅顏薄命的眼鏡女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 我是深水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 不好意思剛才不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個 剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}老爸也說真是對不起那個小姑娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也要道個歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是我自己搞錯了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}現在要來我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是你有空的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}老爸想親自下廚給你壓壓驚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}親自下廚？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}老爸長年單身生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}廚藝不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你找我有事不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呃 雖然是有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也有件事一定要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}知道我家在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呃 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我叫深水透子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 我來隨便做點吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就當是小點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驅 你就先陪陪深水同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}畢竟她今天也算是我的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不要怠慢了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那首先 請去我的房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我的房間在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}前陣子 就是 下陣雨那天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在麒麟館那條坡上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是不是我去抱高山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}而是扶住了她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你知道她那天腳上有傷的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這件事到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}然後 她在坡上差點摔倒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 也不是什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過今天我找你來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也是因為高山的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}高山看起來要跟井美雪哉告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是說 高山看起來要跟井美雪哉告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什麼 什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你怎麼會連小柳的這種事情都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你看到未來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她本人告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}還拜託我告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這件事 想請你告訴透子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}理由是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}理由就不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}石膏像可不能說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼樣 驅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}趁這個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你也辦台手機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}會方便很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是嗎 有那麼方便嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 確實是吧 沒有手機說不定就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有人會跟我打電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳的腳已經好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是嗎 那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒是姐姐你啊 就因為男朋友在住院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就建構起這麼強大的醫院情報網了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}去了多少次醫院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一週三天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是當然 我們簡直就是天生一對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}畢竟他父母是帶著孩子的再婚夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在那複雜的家庭環境裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我們的心兒宛若秋風之中的一片樹葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}又好比風雨中的一葉扁舟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}盡受折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}夠了 給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好朋友…之拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真是承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}前陣子 找到了一個挺有意思的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}發現的時候 怎麼都想要哪天帶你去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要現在就去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等我一下 馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天真是多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}相當美味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}拜託你跟你爸爸說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我這就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}還沒跟我說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}柳 你沒回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 休息處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}稍事休息 補充水與食物之類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}為接下來做準備的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你這不是沒帶水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有點事情想跟小雪說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喜歡小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我知道小雪喜歡透子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也知道你已經跟她告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也清楚要是被小雪拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就沒辦法像再以前那樣幸福地生活在同一個屋簷下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我們 就如小雪所說是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪的回答我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}或許我該說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是小雪放棄透子選擇我的話我會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是你也會看不起我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過我還是要說出口來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雖然我不知道我們的將來會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但這裡是 我今後前進的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想在此告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在家裡拜託還像以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天聽到了一句
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在車站擦肩而過的女高中生說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她說啊 1221年是承久之亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:19.48,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\be2\an7\fs49.5\fad(300,300)}承久之亂是日本鎌倉時代承久3年（1221年）\N後鳥羽上皇為打倒鎌倉幕府舉兵討幕，\N卻失敗遭到鎮壓的兵亂。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}女高中生也真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}陽菜 去拿筷子什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐 來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐 吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================NEXT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}因為我想親口說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這種話 說明不了什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我真是個名副其實的大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我到底算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}來校園裡 我們把話說清楚
